''"das '''Abendrot'''"'' ('''''Abendroth'''''; old form) means evening glow, [[sunset]], [[twilight]].

''"abend"'' means [[evening]].

"Das Abendrot" is the last poem of ''[[Four Last Songs]]'', composed by [[Richard Strauss]], written by [[Joseph von Eichendorff]].

== Surname ==

'''Abendroth''' is a German [[surname]].

Formen/Schreibweisen: de ''[[Abenrode]]'' (um 1250), ''[[Abendrott]]'' (um 1487), ''[[Obentrett]]''

